# Local document cache.
#
# The canonical mock documents live in the SHARED folder at the repo root:
#     ../../../data/mock_docs/
#
# The RAG pipeline reads from MOCK_DOCS_PATH (default: <repo root>/data/mock_docs).
# When the real Google Drive integration is wired up, downloaded files will be
# cached here. Keep this file so the empty folder is tracked in git.
